HPSS Quick Start

http://www.sdsc.edu/us/resources/hpss/

Create file ~/.hsirc:
  authmethod = keytab
  principal = ux451302
  keytab = %H/.private/.ktb_ux451302

Single-Line:
  hsi p <local-file> : <hpss-file>
  hsi g <hpss-file> : <local-file>

Interactive:
  hsi
  help
  p -r <local-file>
  g -r <hpss-file>
  rm -R <hpss-file>
  quit

